      <p class="hero-tagline">Climate risk, energy systems, and applied ML</p>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Building tools for compound extremes, grid constraints, and
        reinforcement learning — from ERA5 reanalysis to LP dispatch
        in the browser.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-links">
        <a href="https://github.com/AlfieMcGlennon" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="GitHub">
